T02TD2340E:305b-1: sarba siddhi ka ro n'a ma /
T02TD2340E:305b-3: thams cad grub par byed pa zhes bya ba /
T02TD2340E:305b-4: grub pa mchog la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2340E:305b-5: bkra shis la sogs rim pas kyang //
T02TD2340E:305b-6: rnal 'byor ltad mo rab brjod bya //
T02TD2340E:305b-7: dang po gza' bkra shis shar ba'i dus su /
T02TD2340E:305b-9: me thun tshod gcig / sa chu tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-11: mtshan mo'i dang po me thun tshod gcig /
T02TD2340E:305b-12: sa thun tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-16: gza' lhag pa shar ba'i dus su /
T02TD2340E:305b-17: sa thun tshod gcig / rlung chu chod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-18: me thun tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-20: mtshan mo chu chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-21: sa thun tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-26: me thun tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-27: sa thun tshod gcig / chu chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-29: mtshan mo me thun tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-30: sa thun tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-34: me thun tshod gcig / sa thun tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-38: mtshan mo sa thun tshod gcig dang /
T02TD2340E:305b-41: me thun tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:305b-43: gza' spen pa shar ba na /
T02TD2340E:306a-3: me thun tshod gcig / sa thun tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:306a-5: mtshan mo rlung chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:306a-6: me thun tshod gcig / sa thun chod gcig / chu chu tshod gnyis so //
T02TD2340E:306a-7: gza' nyi ma shar ba na /
T02TD2340E:306a-10: me thun tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:306a-11: sa thun tshod gcig / chu chu tshod gnyis so //
T02TD2340E:306a-12: mtshan mo rlung chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:306a-13: me thun tshod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:306a-14: sa thun tshod gcig chu chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:306a-17: me thun chod gcig / sa thun chod gcig dang chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:306a-21: mtshan mo sa thun tshod gcig / chu chu tshod gnyis /
T02TD2340E:306a-23: me thun tshod gcig / sa thun tshod gcig go //
T02TD2340E:306a-25: rlung dang me gnyis spang bar bya'o //
T02TD2340E:306a-27: rlung gi bya ba thams cad rmongs par 'gyur zhing /
T02TD2340E:306a-28: chu dang sa'i las brgyad po mtha' dag shes bya ste /
T02TD2340E:306a-29: de ltar shes nas me dang rlung spang bar bya'o //
T02TD2340E:306a-30: rgyal po dbang bskur ba dang /
T02TD2340E:306a-32: bag ma bya ba dang rab tu gnas pa'i las rnams las gtso bo'o //
T02TD2340E:306a-33: mig sman dang ril bu dang mchil lham gnyis dang /
T02TD2340E:306a-34: ral gri dang mchod yon dang zhabs bsil dang gtsug phud dang g-yul dang gsad pa dang zas dang mdzod dang dgon pa bya ba rnams las gtso bo'o //
T02TD2340E:306a-36: slong ba la me gtso bo'o //
T02TD2340E:306a-37: bskrad pa la rlung gtso bo'o //
T02TD2340E:306a-38: rengs pa dang dgug pa la chu gtso bo ste /
T02TD2340E:306a-39: zhi ba'i las dang rgyas pa las gtso bo'o //
T02TD2340E:306a-40: ltad mo dang bstan bcos rtsom pa dang gtsang bar byed pa yang ngo //
T02TD2340E:306a-41: las thams cad grub par byed pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2340E:306a-43: // / tsarba ti'i zhabs kyis mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2340E:306a-44: dge slong rgya mtshos bsgyur ba'o /
